Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:12.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've gone through every book in Ponyville, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and there isn't a single mention of the mysterious chest that came from the Tree of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nor anything about the keys to unlock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:25.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But something tells me that opening it is pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I hope Princess Celestia has some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:32.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If the library in Canterlot doesn't have anything, I don't know where else to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:37.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dearest Twilight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:41.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while it would be perfectly lovely to have you in Canterlot once more,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have another option in mind, much closer to Ponyville.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:49.07,Celestia,,0,0,0,,As you know, the ancient castle that I once shared with Princess Luna,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:53.32,Celestia,,0,0,0,,lies mostly in ruins deep in the Everfree forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:58.11,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But if you look carefully you may find a book that could prove helpful to your research,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:01.42,Celestia,,0,0,0,,hidden somewhere in what's left of the castle library.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at all these ancient books!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's a veritable goldmine of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:13.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,ready to head to home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:26.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This place is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:20.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna move, you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There is no way I'm moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:29.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is the most daring dare anypony ever dared dare another pony in a dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.18,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Uh, whatcha all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash and Applejack are competing for the title of most daring pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is the final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"The Bee Stare"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Last pony to blink wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.14,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need my bees back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:54.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But then we'll never find out who the most daring pony is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:05.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, ladies, I've been keeping excellent score all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:09.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hmm, move to decimal, carry the two and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! You're tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Tied?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:16.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You can't be tied for the most daring pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:19.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't know! Numbers don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:26.91,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'd love to stay and keep keeping score, but I promised to help test the new school bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:29.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I get to ring it all week non-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:33.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And I don't even have to take turns, because no one else volunteered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ok, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We just have to come up with another daring dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think I might have an idea what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:55.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rarity? Don't you think it's a little late in the day to be walking through the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.39,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It is star spider season, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:02.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Though, I'm sure you have a very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:06.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Simply the most important reason I've ever had in my entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, well then I'm happy to help. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:13.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumours that the Castle of the Two Sisters is filled
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:17.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,with the most gorgeous of ancient tapestries in all of pony history!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:21.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It pains me to think of those magnificent creations rotting away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,in those old ruins, totally unappreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:29.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I require your help in borrowing one or two
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,to bring back to the boutique where I can restore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:36.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll even use the patterns as an inspiration for a new line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That does sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes! Well... umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:45.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Maybe not the most important thing in my entire life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but retro-ancient classical will be all the rage the next season,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,so it's nothing to sneeze at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you need those tapestries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:07.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Although, I must admit these ruins are a fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And look at all the dirt everywhere! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:27.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's practically an artistic treasure trove of ancient good taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel! Oh, you really shouldn't have run out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:35.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Ancient ruins are filled with the sorts of things that can hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You could stub your toe, or trip on a loose stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll need all these candles, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,I was really only scared for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:52.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, these aren't for you, Spike. We're gonna be studying late into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And we're gonna need all the light we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Eh, what's so daring about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,This is where we got the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,When I was just a filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:10.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith told me of an ancient legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.74,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,When Nightmare Moon was banished,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:16.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,not every last bit of her dark magic went with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny used to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"When night falls on the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,that magic takes the form of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,the Pony of Shadows!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You mean like a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:32.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nopony kno~o~ows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This one is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,it certainly could use some restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Be dear, fly up there and lift it off that hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Maybe from below?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's so daring about an old legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:07.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Plus, I don't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You might want to rethink your position on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You saw that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ru-u-un!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Ough! I think I hurt my wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my dear, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:38.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This tapestry is far too heavy. We'll just have to find a smaller one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Where pray tell did you disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:47.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,While you were struggling under that fabric, the entire wall spun around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You must have activated a secret door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:55.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I suppose these ruins are choke full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:56.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We must use the utmost care as we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay! So maybe the legend is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why I brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess, only the most daring pone of all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,could stay in this castle all night without being scared off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Scared? I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:28.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whoever stays in the castle the longest is the most daring pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:37.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But it's gonna take a lot more than some shadowy ghost pony to get me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Find anything, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,Eh, nope, nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:57.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Angel? What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"The Journal of the Two Sisters."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is the book Princess Celestia was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I sure hope you're not afraid of the dark, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:27.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But even if I was, I'd be at least fifty percent less scared of it than you, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:31.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know how that math works, because i'm not scared at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:44.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's just a dark hallway full of disembodied pony legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:48.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nothing creepy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:55.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to wonder if maybe this castle doesn't want my expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:57.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:58.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rarity, have you seen them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure he made the trip down with us, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:08.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh goodness, we have to find him. An ancient castle is no place for a bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:12.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He can get hit by falling debris, or a floor can give out under him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:16.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He can be trapped in a dark place with no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine how that might feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If you're scared, you can just admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,you don't need to put your hoof around me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:44.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I felt something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, tapestries or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have had just about enough of secret passages,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:06.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,mysterious presences and unappreciative castles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.12,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But we can't leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:12.38,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now with the Angel lost somewhere in this dangerous old castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He can be trapped under crumbling statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:20.97,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Or stuck high in a tower without food or water or any friends at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, you've got to hear this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love to duck behind the paintings,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and though the hall of hooves still gives her a bit of a fright,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the trap door slide is Luna's favorite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hall of hooves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"Soon the organ to the outside will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:44.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's the "organ to the outside"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:58.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,the creepy sound of a haunted pipe organ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know what are you talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Did you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Quit being such a scaredy dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:23.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This castle is thousands of years old and half of it was destroyed by Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course it makes strange sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's practically falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,O-kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.13,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, we'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Did you find Angel? Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They are perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:55.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No castle in it's right mind can possibly object to my restoring such exquisite works of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,They are lovely, Rarity, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I have to keep looking for Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't think, I given up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.38,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Do you think there is a single room in this castle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,that isn't filled with terrifying things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's just old pony armor. What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's gonna come to live or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:30.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now you look here, castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You're very old and very scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but your wall art is in an atrocious state!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:29.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And there is nothing you can do to keep me from my sacred task of restoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:37.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If you went back to Ponyville, that means I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:37.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know hiding isn't really your sense of humor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but please let this be a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess if I don't find you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I win by default, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:34.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of all the castles in Equestria this is by far the most ungrateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I hope you two are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Haunted statues, creepy armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on castle, is that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to restore ancient art...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:45.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,probably just more strange sounds of this old castle falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No one likes sarcasm, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,What got into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's okay Аngel, you're okay, you're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Shadows everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Ange-e-el!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Alright, everypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Must.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Save.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Have you all spent the whole night running around, scaring each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, that depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:41.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:46.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,On whether or not you are the Pony of Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's the Pony of Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just an old pony's tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then who's playing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're going to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.63,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,A Pony of Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:49.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey you guys! Did you know I can totally play the organ? Because I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Pinkie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're the Pony of Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The pony of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See? What'd I tell ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I though you were to ring the school bell all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:05.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. I only had to ring it for like five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They said that was good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.41,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Can't imagine why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So then, I decided to throw a "Finish ringing the school bell" party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But I didn't have any bluebells, and you can't throw a "Finish ringing the school bell" party without bluebells,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,so I went to Everfree Forest to pick some, but it started to get so chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I had to wrap myself up in the tarp I was gonna use to carry the flowers, and then I saw Fluttershy and Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:29.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But they went into the castle before I could invite them to my party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:33.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I followed them inside so I can help you all with your party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What party is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:40.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The "Everypony come to the scary old castle and hide from each other while I play the organ" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I swear, this is going right back where I found it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,just as soon as I've returned it to its former glory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now don't go running off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:02.74,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oooh, I can't believe I was so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.69,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Guess I let my imagination get the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think we all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.04,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I always let my imagination run away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Then it comes back, with cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:17.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, it's good to know that whenever your imagination is getting away from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,a good friend can help you rein it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And even though I didn't find anything out about the mysterious chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was here to help all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You certainly did that, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Why weren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Reading Celestia's diary made it hard to be afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:36.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,because I knew what it was like when she and Luna lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:41.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Knowing something about the past made it easier to deal with my problems in the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Even the scary ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just thought of a great idea!
